I'll also add that as an enchanter, I've reverse-kited many times with great success (SoW is needed, though). I can easily grab taunt from my pet, then run around in circles while the pet does all the work and stays healthy. This may not seem to apply much to a beastlord, but if your health drops below 1 bub and you're all out of mana, you can pull the same stunt. I've done this a few times already with my BST and it works great. <p><p align="center"><a href="http://pub75.ezboard.com/btheshoemakers"><img src="http://www.pwshift.com/tr/images/fimble_transparent.gif" alt="Fimble Fetishists!" align="center" border="0"></a><BR>email: <a href="mailto:FimblePiddlebitz@hotmail.com">FimblePiddlebitz@hotmail.com</a><BR>AIM: FimbleMT</p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=7.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=7.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.tdtccomputers.com/morellthulebbs/addreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm19.threadControl?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/techops.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm19.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=7.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 bord